description.displayText:
I highly recommend Catalina for the job posting in your company. Integrity in thoughts, teamwork and punctuality are some of her best known qualities that I have found to be her valuable assets in the long years of our friendship. We have both volunteer in several church and community related projects; some of these projects were coordination of youth groups ages 15 to 24, homeless shelters, and food pantry. We also helped with activities of daily living to sick parish and community members. 
Catalina is organized, efficient, extremely competent, and has an excellent rapport with people of all ages. Her communication skills, both written and verbal, are excellent.
Catalina would be a great asset to your company.
